data.description: This stunning home offers a versatile layout with two spacious bedrooms and an additional room that can be customized to suit your needs, whether it be a home gym, mother-in-law suite, or an extra bedroom. With three bathrooms, there will never be a wait for a shower or a morning rush. Situated conveniently close to the Greenville Hospital and Downtown Greenville, you'll have easy access to all the amenities this vibrant city has to offer. The backyard boasts a generous deck, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying a peaceful evening. Plus, the storage building in the back provides ample space for all your belongings. With new windows on the back part of the home and a brand new water heater, and a freshly paved concrete driveway, this home is move-in ready. Don't miss out on this opportunity.  Being sold "As Is". Schedule your showing today.
